These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta
2 different pets are kept: rat, ferret
The people have 2 different jobs:  dressmaker, musician
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the musician##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Beverage      | coffee  | fanta   |
| Pet   | ferret     | rat   |
| Job         | musician | dressmaker |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
There are 2 different nationalities: indonesian, mexican
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, skydiving
1. the mexican is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Nationality           | mexican         | indonesian     |
| Hobby     | board-games   | skydiving    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, red
There 2 different types of food: potato, grapes
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
2. the person eating grapes is on the right of the person who likes red##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Color         | red | chestnut    |
| Food         | potato         | grapes        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

