.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, helicopter
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, blood-red
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Transport      | helicopter     | motorbike |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Color         | purple | blood-red     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

