.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-6::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, electrician
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daffodil, poppy
2 different pets are kept: cat, horse
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, october
1. the person who's birthday is in october is in an even position##4
2. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
3. the electrician is the person who growsdaffodil##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Job           | electrician | coach    |
| Flower   | daffodil       | poppy |
| Pet           | cat         | horse    |
| Birthday         | april    | october   |

