The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
2. the person eating peas is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
4. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Hobby         | writing   | rock-climbing |
| Pet           | snake | hedgehog    |
| Food   | peas      | blueberry         |
| Sport         | sailing   | weightlifting |

