.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, water
There 2 different types of food: blueberry, orange
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: tulip, dahlia
1. the person eating orange is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate | water    |
| Food         | orange        | blueberry |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Flower   | tulip        | dahlia     |

 